data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION PENDING SHORT SALE APPROVAL !!!!!!! SOLAR, SOLAR, SOLAR..... One less utility bill to stress over with this home!!!! PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!!! Welcome to this exquisite 3-bed, 3-bath home on a 1.41-acre lot. With two master suites, optimal privacy awaits. Dive into the pool, or soak in the hot tub and savor serene lakefront views. The fenced property offers security, while mature oak trees provide charm and shade. A two-car garage and newer appliances enhance convenience. Embrace sustainability with the solar system, reducing energy costs. This tranquil retreat combines modern comforts, natural beauty, and seclusion. Don't miss this remarkable opportunity.
